der-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0;Margin:0;font-size:0px\"><img src=\"https://email-static.useinsider.com/f940abcdc21d4566ac97b97fb4e8650f/lib/pluginId_f940abcdc21d4566ac97b97fb4e8650f_bancontactproduction_images/header_newsletter_april_eng.png\" width=\"600\" class=\"adapt-img\" style=\"display:block;font-size:14px;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;margin:0;border-radius:10px\" alt=\"\"/></td>\r\n </tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr>\r\n <tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"left\" style=\"padding:20px 20px 0;Margin:0\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" role=\"none\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px\"><tbody><tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0;Margin:0;width:560px\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px\"><tbody><tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"left\" class=\"es-m-text\" style=\"padding:10px 0 0;Margin:0\"><h1 style=\"Margin:0;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';mso-line-height-rule:exactly;letter-spacing:0;font-size:26px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:120%;color:#0b2265\"><strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">Hello Denys,</strong></h1>\r\n<p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#333333;font-size:14px\"><br/></p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">Many of you have been asking for it, and we’ve listened. The popular ‘Pay a Contact’ feature is officially back in the Bancontact Pay app!</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\"> </p>\r\n <p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">Whether you’ve missed the feature over the past few months or are discovering it for the first time: from now on, you no longer need an IBAN to initiate a payment. You take the initiative yourself, wherever and whenever you like.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\" class=\"es-content\" role=\"none\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px;width:100%;table-layout:fixed !important\"><tbody><tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0;Margin:0\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"transparent\" class=\"es-footer-body\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px;background-color:transparent;width:600px\" role=\"none\"><tbody><tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"left\" style=\"padding:20px 20px 0;Margin:0\"><!--[if mso]><table style=\"width:560px\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"width:366px\" valign=\"top\"><![endif]--><table align=\"left\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"es-left es-m-p20b\" role=\"none\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px;float:left\"><tbody><tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"left\" style=\"padding:0;Margin:0;width:366px\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px\"><tbody><tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"left\" style=\"padding:0;Margin:0\"><h2 style=\"Margin:0;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';mso-line-height-rule:exactly;letter-spacing:0;font-size:20px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:120%;color:#0439d1;text-align:left\"><b>Why you’ll love this feature</b></h2>\r\n<p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#0b2265;font-size:14px\"><br/></p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\"><strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">👉 Complete freedom</strong>: settle last night’s bill or send some pocket money to the kids without waiting for an account number or payment request.</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">​</p>\r\n <p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">👉 <strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">Your contact list is your payment list</strong>: link the contacts on your smartphone and see straight away who you can pay via the app.</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">​</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">👉 <strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">Choose your card</strong>: add up to five cards from different banks and pick your favourite for each payment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">​</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">👉 <strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">Pay remotely</strong>: you don’t need to be physically together. Search for the name of the person you want to pay in the app, enter the amount, and that’s it.</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\"> </p>\r\n <p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">Discover the feature today on your app’s home screen!</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n <!--[if mso]></td><td style=\"width:20px\"></td>\r\n<td style=\"width:174px\" valign=\"top\"><![endif]--><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"right\" class=\"es-right\" role=\"none\" style=\"mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px;float:right\"><tbody><tr style=\"border-colla