0;font-size:14px\"><strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">✔️ </strong>Help us tailor features to your needs by sharing your experiences.</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\"><strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">​</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\"><strong style=\"font-weight:700 !important\">✔️ </strong>Get a unique behind-the-scenes look and have a say in how the app evolves.</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">​</p><p style=\"Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:arial, 'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; mso-font-alt: 'Arial';line-height:150%;letter-spacing:0;color:#000000;font-size:14px\">Interested? Sign up as a beta tester today!</p></td></tr>\r\n <tr style=\"border-collapse:collapse\"><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0;Margin:0\"><!--[if mso]><a href=\"https://u34711340.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=u001.qfk-2F8BU3E9Ihr1chzhuUYMtVsRvNqjZuhNIas9rWrAf9VYsx74Jx1XsY50x99Av0eq7jTqhS6J1udQdSZ93-2FI3W-2BYtwxeTWVNGZCa-2BR218I-3D59oE_iIMeJ8gE4unUr1PufjNeeLc6ySPDnCLnxb8ygD817xvzw8YJlVgkJqj5CqKe3aW50Sgm3DbOioKLH4gJR3iEd-2FeIZ4cq76CiVMxD01gqO8qtiCneuEXb3MRn5cbdftOT70NxxllPfzdhTFEkL9wwuvxLEsKCQEG-2BYVYttrVk2clllxJ9tCOIbCN3HDzx-2FTmFnlICUHTI0FcyvIMnZ1hmiD3u9nLnLs1LJyx6d7L-2F0gpnSDk4HST7dby5QbrnYpANJuGEzq7NvwQL5zce71tygWKikwdE5jLrfC4q57bjYx-2FC4pIj8j3YbwoWtsL-2BMWBkpql36OOcW0-2BKw0Xo-2BMEQ-2BN2Q5XRTTXdpy9-2Bq0WFMijur94-2F6QLkbqPOimkZiZjTQg1UPcOd1qz1D5JQLXdmYxhmNfbUu4-2F9UnS